<?php ?><div align="left">tinyeditor is a module which integrates TinyMCE, a platform independent web based Javascript HTML WYSIWYG editor control, into Xoops CMS.<br />It is released as Open Source under GPL and allows you and your users to have a comfortable way to write content on your site.<br /> It has the ability to convert html textarea fields to editor instances.<br />
It comes bundled with an advanced Image manager and a Link-to-content dialog which quickly add links to your published content.<br />
Last but not least it's fully configurable via module's config options.<br />
Nice xoopsing, ralf57 and frankblack.
